{"tid":937681,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[真天使] IU獲得第18回「令人驕傲的韓國人大賞」的「捐贈天使」獎","createTime":"2018-12-11T17:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T12:32:53.000Z","uid":34643,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"954b16e33e2f6faa9b6f9001c2dfbd3e9410db5a","tid":937681,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"11日,韓國媒體人聯合會公開了第18屆&lt;引以為榮韓國人大賞&gt;12組獲獎者.其中藝人有#防彈少年團[超話]#獲得&quot;弘揚國威音樂部門&quot;獎項,IU獲得&quot;捐贈天使&quot;部門獎項等.此外,頒獎禮將於韓國時間12日下午2時30分在汝矣島舉辦. ​<br />\n<br />\n歷年捐款：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fy2x7t79daj30ku113wo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fy2x7t79daj30ku113wo3.jpg&h=0af6f350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18年年初先是為聾啞老人捐贈5千萬韓元，之後又為困難兒童捐贈了一億韓元，並在出道紀念日以與Uaena的共同名義捐贈了一億韓元<br />\n<br />\n我們人美心善的小天使實至名歸"},{"pid":"57bcc6a4df80857e4a35499dde3e27163b2ddb00","tid":937681,"uid":34643,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fy2htnrc6vj311o1h718c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fy2htnrc6vj311o1h718c.jpg&h=4bc78a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fy2htn7hogj312m1i519g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fy2htn7hogj312m1i519g.jpg&h=dd25c9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fy2hto72lqj31391jnarm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fy2hto72lqj31391jnarm.jpg&h=c61c197d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fy2hton4x3j31381i9qis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fy2hton4x3j31381i9qis.jpg&h=b17a1824&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid"